約翰·魯本等人在數個研究中指出<ref name="RubenJonesEtAl1997LungStructure" /><ref name="RubenJonesEtAl1998LungVentilationAndGasExchange">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Ruben, J.A., Jones, T.D., Geist, N.R., Leitch, A., and Hillenius, W.J. |title=Lung ventilation and gas exchange in theropod dinosaurs |journal=Science |volume=278 |issue=5341 |pages=1267–1270 |doi=10.1126/science.278.5341.1267 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/short/278/5341/1267 |year=1997 |access-date=2008-11-17 |archive-date=2008-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523115409/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/short/278/5341/1267 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RubenDalSassoEtAl1999PulmonaryFunction" /><ref name="RubenHilleniusEtAl1996MetabolicStatus">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Ruben, J.A., Hillenius, W.J., Geist, N.R., Leitch, A., Jones, T.D., Currie, P.J., Horner, J.R., and Espe, G. |title=The metabolic status of some Late Cretaceous dinosaurs |journal=Science |volume=273 |issue=5279 |pages=1204–1207 |doi=10.1126/science.273.5279.1204 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/273/5279/1204 |format=abstract page |date=August 1996 |access-date=2008-11-17 |archive-date=2009-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226152618/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/273/5279/1204 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RubenJones2000FurAndFeathers">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Ruben, J.A., and Jones, T.D. |title=Selective Factors Associated with the Origin of Fur and Feathers |journal=American Zoologist |year=2000 |volume=40 |issue=4 |pages=585–596 |doi=10.1093/icb/40.4.585 |url=http://icb.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/40/4/585 |access-date=2008-10-13 |archive-date=2009-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829095340/http://icb.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/40/4/585 |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
* 沒有恐龍化石曾發現鼻甲，包含[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]]。
* 所以已發現具有鼻管的恐龍，由於鼻管短、狹窄，無法容納鼻甲。
* 根據以上特徵，恐龍的肺部乾燥，無法具有哺乳類與鳥類的呼吸頻率，以及高的代謝率。

然而，目前已出現數個反對意見：
* 某些鳥類（[[鴕鳥目|鴕鳥目]]、[[鸌形目|鸌形目]]、[[隼形目|隼形目]]）與哺乳類（[[鯨魚|鯨魚]]、[[穿山甲|穿山甲]]、[[蝙蝠|蝙蝠]]、大象、大部分[[靈長類|靈長類]]）也缺乏呼吸用鼻甲，或者鼻甲非常小<ref name="Bang1966">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Bang, B.G.  | year=1966 | title=The olfactory apparatus of Procellariiformes |journal=Acta Anatomica | volume=65 | pages=391–415 |doi=10.1159/000142884 }}</ref><ref name="Bang1977">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Bang, B.G.  | year=1971 | title=  Functional anatomy of the olfactory system in 23 orders of birds |journal=Acta Anatomica | volume=79 (supplement 58) | pages=1–76}}</ref><ref name="Scott1954">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Scott, J.H. | year=1954 | title=Heat regulating function of the nasal mucous membrane |journal=Journal of Larynology and Otology | volume=68 |pages=308–317}}</ref><ref name="Coulombeetal1965">{{{en}}{{cite journal 
|author=Coulombe, H.N., Sam H. Ridgway, S.H.,  and Evans, W.E. | year=1965 | title=Respiratory water exchange in two species of porpoise | journal=Science | volume=149 | issue=3679 | pages=86–88 | doi=10.1126/science.149.3679.86}}</ref>，卻是[[內溫性|內溫性]]動物，其中少部分甚至是非常靈活的動物。
* 不同的科學家提出，已發現鼻管的恐龍，牠們的鼻管長又寬，足以容納鼻甲，或是類似的防止肺臟乾燥的器官<ref name="Witmer2001NostrilPosition">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Witmer, L.M. |title=Nostril Position in Dinosaurs and Other Vertebrates and Its Significance for Nasal Function |journal=Science |issue=5531 |pages=850–853 |doi=10.1126/science.1062681 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/293/5531/850 |volume=293 |format=abstract page |pmid=11486085 |date=August 2001 |access-date=2008-11-17 |archive-date=2008-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080726152713/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/293/5531/850 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 鼻甲是種非常脆弱的結構，不太可能在化石化的過程中保存下來。目前的鳥類化石，都沒有發現過鼻甲。

== 心血管系統 ==
[[File:Willoheart.jpg|thumb]]化石，可能具有石化的心臟]]
科學家普遍認為，恐龍的血壓相當高，才能將血液輸送到高舉的頭部，因此恐龍應具有四腔室[[心臟|心臟]]，[[心室|心室]]已經分為左右兩邊。但是，[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]的[[肺臟|肺臟]]無法在過高的血壓下運作良好<ref name="ReidInFarlowBrettSurman1997" />。在2000年，一個名為「Willo」的[[奇異龍|奇異龍]]化石，被發現有四腔室心臟與一個[[主動脈|主動脈]]的痕跡，目前正存放在[[北卡羅萊納自然科學博物館|北卡羅萊納自然科學博物館]]。研究人員根據心臟結構，認為奇異龍有較高的代謝效率，並非[[變溫動物|變溫動物]]<ref name=FRSBHK00>{{en}}{{cite journal |last=Fisher |first=Paul E. |coauthors=Russell, Dale A.; Stoskopf, Michael K.; Barrick, Reese E.; Hammer, Michael; and Kuzmitz, Aandrew A. |title=Cardiovascular evidence for an intermediate or higher metabolic rate in an ornithischian dinosaur |journal=Science |volume=288 |issue=5465 |pages=503–505 |doi=10.1126/science.288.5465.503 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/reprint/288/5465/503.pdf?ijkey=c75f52279333bdb9fa3d0504b786c07f9e35e2f9 |accessdate=2007-03-10 |date=April 2000 |archive-date=2007-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001020817/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/reprint/288/5465/503.pdf?ijkey=c75f52279333bdb9fa3d0504b786c07f9e35e2f9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們的結論已遭到否定；其他研究人員公佈了一個研究，宣稱這顆類似心臟的物質，其實是個[[結石|結石]]。他們認為這個物體的結構令人誤解，例如所謂的主動脈結構雖然進入心臟結構，但缺乏所連接的[[動脈|動脈]]、主動脈與心臟的連接處最為狹窄；實際上，該物體與一根[[肋骨|肋骨]]連接，中心有同心圓層，右腿也有一樣的同心圓層<ref name=RMS01>{{en}}{{cite journal |last=Rowe |first=Timothy |coauthors=McBride, Earle F.; and Sereno, Paul C. |title=Technical comment: dinosaur with a heart of stone |journal=Science |volume=291 |issue=5505 |pages=p. 783a |doi=10.1126/science.291.5505.783a |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/291/5505/783a |accessdate=2007-03-10 |date=February 2001 |archive-date=2007-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070906213804/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/291/5505/783a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而最初提出石化心臟的研究人員捍衛他們的理論，他們同意有某種形式的同心圓層存在，但其中一層則包圍了心臟與主動脈的肌肉部位<ref name=RFBS01>{{en}}{{cite journal |last=Russell |first=Dale A. |coauthors=Fisher, Paul E.; Barrick, Reese E.; and Stoskopf, Michael K. |title=Reply: dinosaur with a heart of stone |journal=Science |volume=291 |issue=5505 |pages=p. 783a |doi=10.1126/science.291.5505.783a |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/291/5505/783a |accessdate=2007-03-10 |date=February 2001 |archive-date=2007-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070906213804/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/291/5505/783a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

這顆疑似石化心臟的物體是否可以反映奇異龍的代謝率與內部結構，仍然沒有定論。現代鱷魚與鳥類都擁有四腔室心臟（鱷魚的心臟較不一樣），所以恐龍可能也有類似的心臟結構；而心臟結構與代謝率沒有必然的關係<ref name=CH04>{{en}}Chinsamy, Anusuya; and Hillenius, Willem J. (2004). "Physiology of nonavian dinosaurs". ''The Dinosauria'', 2nd. 643–659.</ref>。

== 成長率 ==
